      "id": "d570dd34",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "Con esto, ya podemos aplicar nuestro modelo:"
      ],
      "id": "7a8284fd"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "# Instanciamos nuestro modelo.\n",
        "model = LogisticRegression(\n",
        "    penalty=\"elasticnet\", l1_ratio=0.5, solver=\"saga\", random_state=42,\n",
        ")\n",
        "\n",
        "# Y luego lo entrenamos.\n",
        "model.fit(X_train, y_train)"
      ],
      "id": "a9737f19",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "Ahora tomemos una imagen cualquiera del conjunto de entrenamiento y verifiquemos a qué número representa:"
